WebView2
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

mullion does not bundle, redistribute or derive from any WebView2 binding.

The COM layer in internal/webview2 - runtime discovery, environment creation, the
interface definitions and the event handlers - is written against Microsoft's
published WebView2 interface definitions. No binary is embedded and no loader DLL
is shipped.

The Microsoft Edge WebView2 Runtime itself is a system component that must be
present on the target machine. mullion locates the installed runtime and calls
into it; it does not distribute it.
